title: Upgrade migration recipe not sending telemetry pings
body:
In contrast to other recipes, https://normandy-admin.prod.mozaws.net/control/recipe/25/ (last enabled ~6 days ago) has not pinged telemetry with any data - no data are found where the surveyId in the payload == 'out-of-date-3'

[see Spark gist](https://gist.github.com/jtg567/36f1fdb0e1db13113a435c8b32aeda6c), compare cells 6 and 7
